<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 6 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">You don't need to memorise 279,000 words to dramatically improve at Scrabble. The biggest gains come from mastering a handful of high-leverage skills — the same approach tournament players used to go from casual to competitive in months rather than years.</p>

<p>This guide focuses on the fastest path to measurable improvement. Follow the priority order below, dedicate 15 minutes daily, and you'll see your average score climb within two weeks.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">The 80/20 Improvement Path</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
